Installation instructions
-------------------------

    1. Install FEniCS 1.3 from http://fenicsproject.org/
    2. Install dolfin-adjoint 1.3 from http://www.dolfin-adjoint.org/
    3. Install the most recent version of libspud from the Fluidity project https://github.com/FluidityProject/fluidity
    4. Clone this repository and include its root path to $PYTHONPATH


Simulation scripts
------------------

* Section 2.5 Forward model verifiction
    Directory tests/similarity
    Run with "python similarity.py"




